Description_lang: Transforms the target (Warning: target safety in future parchment) into a chicken, wandering around incapacitated for $d. While affected, the victim cannot take actions but will regenerate health very quickly. Damage will cancel the effect. Limit 1.Only works on Beasts, Humanoids and Critters level 60 or lower. Only usable outdoors in the Shadowlands.
AuraDescription_lang: Incapacitated. Cannot attack or cast spells.
